<Subtitle>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>1</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>10122</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>19166</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>那天晚上，杰克告诉了妈妈没有牛奶的事。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>2</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>19166</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>22137</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“这太可怕了！” 妈妈说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>3</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>22137</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>25302</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们以后怎么赚钱呢？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>4</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>25302</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>31688</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她趴在桌子上，哭了起来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>5</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>31688</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>34601</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>杰克非常害怕一件事。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>6</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>34601</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>43346</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>那就是看到妈妈哭。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>7</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>43346</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>47206</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“别哭了，妈妈。” 杰克说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>8</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>47206</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>49960</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我有一个计划。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>9</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>49960</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>52299</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>妈妈抬起头。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>10</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>52299</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>57193</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们出了很大的问题，杰克。” 妈妈说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>11</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>57193</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>62540</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“现在不是说什么大计划的时候。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>12</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>62540</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>65382</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>杰克笑了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>13</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>65382</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>71512</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“不是大计划，这次的计划非常简单！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>14</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>71512</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>75479</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“什么计划？” 妈妈轻声问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>15</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>75479</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>79827</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我会找一份工作，” 杰克说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>16</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>79827</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>83672</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“这样我就能赚钱了。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>17</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>83672</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>86563</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“一份工作？” 妈妈问，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>18</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>86563</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>90472</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你能去哪里找工作？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>19</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>90472</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>94424</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我会去镇上看看。” 杰克说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>20</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>94424</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>98731</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你去年就试过了。” 妈妈说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>21</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>98731</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>108515</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“还记得吗，杰克？没有人需要帮手。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>22</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>108515</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>112244</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“那是一年前的事了，” 杰克说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>23</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>112244</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>115956</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“也许现在有人需要帮手。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>24</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>115956</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>121535</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他耸了耸肩：“试一试也没有什么不好的。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>25</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>121535</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>127597</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>就在这时，外面有什么东西吸引了杰克的目光。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>26</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>127597</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>134395</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>夜空中，一颗星星闪闪发光。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>27</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>134395</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>138347</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>杰克心里充满了希望。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>28</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>138347</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>140983</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>杰克又看向妈妈。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>29</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>140983</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>144306</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我有感觉，妈妈！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>30</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>144306</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>148375</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>这次会有神奇的事情发生。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>31</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>148375</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>152166</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>妈妈叹了口气。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>32</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>152166</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>156433</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“好吧，你去找工作吧。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>33</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>156433</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>165693</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>希望会有什么好事发生。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
</Subtitle>